title: Jolly LLB 2 Grosses 188 Crores Worldwide | Box Office Report
text: tweet Akshay Kumar’s Jolly LLB 2 has managed to perform decently in spite of new releases. The film became Akshay’s first film in 2017 to enter the 100 crore club . It currently stands with a collection of 110.71 crores nett ( 155 crores gross) at the India box office. The film’s overseas collections are approximately 33 crores and now stands with a worldwide collection of 188 crores at the box office. Jolly LLB 2 Grosses 188 Crores Worldwide Directed by Subhash Kapoor, the film also starred Huma Qureshi, Saurabh Shukla and Annu Kapoor in lead roles. TAGS
